milestones.description: Javed Miandad has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (22) for PAK, going past Wasim Bari
Pakistan's 9-run win against West Indies is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 36-run win against England
Sarfraz Nawaz and Zaheer Abbas's 57-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 33 between Saleem Altaf and Wasim Bari
